column4:
['Dekho mera ye jantar mantar', '
Ho jaunga mai yu chu mantar', '
Aaja re aaja ab na kar deri', '
Aata hu mai jan meri', '
Aaja re aaja ab na kar deri', '
Are baitha hu mai potli me', '
Aaja bas ja jadu me tu', '
Dekho mera ye jantar mantar', '
Ho jaunga mai yu chu mantar', 'Anguthi babu ki ungli me', '
Magar ab dekh dhoban ki chunri me hai', '
Anguthi babu ki ungli me', '
Magar ab dekh dhoban ki chunri me hai', '
Ye teri bat sachi hai', '
Jadugar ki tu bachi hai', '
Umar teri kachi hai', '
Kachi hai kachi hai', '
Dekho mera ye jantar mantar', '
Ho jaunga mai yu chu mantar.']
